                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p id="notificationBody" class=" text-center" style="color: white;">It appears you are not a verified StreamTutor! If you are a student, create a separate student account. If you are a StreamTutor, please wait to be approved.</p>
                    <a href="/"><img src="~/images/streamworkPencilWhite.png" style="display:block; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;" height="70"/></a>
